messages.content: What does the ComfyUI Preview Magnifier custom node do?
The ComfyUI Preview Magnifier custom node preview images with a magnifier hosted on the ComfyUI engine.
What is the purpose of the ComfyUI Preview Magominator?
The ComfyUI Preview Magnifier is used for previewing single images with magnification capabilities, comparing two images side by side with a magnifier, and supporting xy-plot with magnification.
How does the ComfyUI Preview Magnifier compare two images?
The ComfyUI Preview Magnifier allows for a side-by-side comparison of two images with an interactive magnifier overlay.
How does the ComfyUI Preview Magnifier handle xy plots?
The ComfyUI Preview Magnifier is capable of displaying xy plots alongside the images for enhanced analysis.
Can the ComfyUI Preview Magnifier be used for single image preview and comparison?
Yes, the ComfyUI Preview Magnifier is capable of previewing single images with magnification and comparing two images side by side with an interactive magnifier.
